---
import Layout from '../../components/Layout.astro';
import { getContent } from '../../utils/content';

const content = await getContent('zh');
---

<Layout title="关于规则 - Pravilo.Club" description="了解古老的规则技术和健康实践" lang="zh">
  <main class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="page-title">关于规则</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">古老的脊柱减压技术，现代健康实践</p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <section class="section history-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">规则的历史</h2>
      <div class="history-content">
        <div class="history-text">
          <p>规则（Pravilo）是一种古老的脊柱减压技术，起源于俄罗斯的传统健康实践。这项技术已经传承了数百年，帮助无数人恢复脊柱健康，改善整体身体状况。</p>
          
          <p>规则不仅仅是一种物理练习，更是一种完整的健康哲学。它结合了身体、心理和精神层面的治疗，帮助人们重新连接自己的身体，恢复内在的平衡和力量。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="history-features">
          <div class="feature">
            <h4>古老智慧</h4>
            <p>传承数百年的传统技术</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <h4>整体治疗</h4>
            <p>身体、心理、精神的综合治疗</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <h4>自然康复</h4>
            <p>利用身体自身的康复能力</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section principles-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">规则的核心原理</h2>
      <div class="principles-grid">
        <div class="principle-card">
          <h3>脊柱减压</h3>
          <p>通过特殊的悬挂技术，减轻脊柱压力，恢复椎间盘的自然状态。</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="principle-card">
          <h3>肌肉放松</h3>
          <p>深度放松紧张的肌肉群，释放长期积累的紧张和压力。</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="principle-card">
          <h3>血液循环</h3>
          <p>改善血液循环，促进营养物质的输送和废物的排出。</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="principle-card">
          <h3>神经功能</h3>
          <p>优化神经系统功能，改善身体各部分的协调性。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section benefits-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">规则的益处</h2>
      <div class="benefits-content">
        <div class="benefits-list">
          <div class="benefit-item">
            <h4>立即效果</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>缓解背部和颈部疼痛</li>
              <li>改善姿势</li>
              <li>增加灵活性</li>
              <li>深度放松</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="benefit-item">
            <h4>长期效果</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>改善血液循环</li>
              <li>增强核心肌肉</li>
              <li>减少慢性疼痛</li>
              <li>提高能量水平</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="benefits-text">
          <p>规则练习适合所有年龄段和体能水平的人。无论你是办公室工作者、运动员，还是正在寻找自然康复方法的人，规则都能为你带来显著的改善。</p>
          
          <p>这项技术特别适合那些长期受到背痛、颈部紧张、姿势问题困扰的人。通过定期的规则练习，你可以重新获得身体的自由和灵活性。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section process-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">规则练习过程</h2>
      <div class="process-steps">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <h3>咨询</h3>
          <p>了解你的目标、问题和期望。评估当前健康状况和姿势。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <h3>准备</h3>
          <p>通过特殊练习和呼吸技巧为身体减压做准备。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <h3>减压</h3>
          <p>在经验丰富的指导者指导下，在规则模拟器上进行主要工作。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">4</div>
          <h3>整合</h3>
          <p>恢复时间和感觉讨论。家庭练习建议。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>准备开始你的规则之旅？</h2>
        <p>体验古老规则技术的力量，重新连接你的身体，恢复内在的平衡和力量。</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/zh/contact" class="btn btn-primary">预约课程</a>
          <a href="/zh/services" class="btn btn-secondary">了解服务</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #1a1a1a 100%);
    color: #ffffff;
    padding: 6rem 0 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #d4af37;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #d4af37;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .history-section {
    background: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .history-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .history-text p {
    color: #cccccc;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .history-features {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature {
    background: #000;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border-left: 4px solid #d4af37;
  }

  .feature h4 {
    color: #d4af37;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .feature p {
    color: #cccccc;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .principles-section {
    background: #000;
  }

  .principles-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .principle-card {
    background: #1a1a1a;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 15px;
    border: 1px solid #333;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .principle-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: #d4af37;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);
  }

  .principle-card h3 {
    color: #d4af37;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .principle-card p {
    color: #cccccc;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .benefits-section {
    background: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .benefits-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .benefits-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .benefit-item {
    background: #000;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border-left: 4px solid #d4af37;
  }

  .benefit-item h4 {
    color: #d4af37;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .benefit-item ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .benefit-item li {
    color: #cccccc;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .benefit-item li:before {
    content: "•";
    color: #d4af37;
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
  }

  .benefits-text p {
    color: #cccccc;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .process-section {
    background: #000;
  }

  .process-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .step {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .step-number {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    background: #d4af37;
    color: #000;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
  }

  .step h3 {
    color: #d4af37;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .step p {
    color: #cccccc;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #000000 100%);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #d4af37;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: #cccccc;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: #d4af37;
    color: #000;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #ff6b35;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: #d4af37;
    border: 2px solid #d4af37;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: #d4af37;
    color: #000;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
    
    .history-content,
    .benefits-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .principles-grid,
    .process-steps {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>
